<mxfile host="app.diagrams.net">
  <diagram name="Trang-1" id="9Rv6-iDLOR9fpCx5fjbM">
    <mxGraphModel dx="9762" dy="4309" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="827" pageHeight="1169" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&quot;data&quot;:&quot;@startuml\nleft to right direction\n!theme amiga\n\n\n\n&#39; --- Tinh chỉnh khoảng cách cho thưa và thoáng ---\nskinparam roundcorner 10\nskinparam nodesep 40      \nskinparam ranksep 150     \nskinparam packageStyle rectangle\n\n&#39; --- BẮT BUỘC PASSENGER BÊN TRÁI ---\nactor \&quot;Passenger\&quot; as passenger\n\n&#39; --- KHUNG HỆ THỐNG TVM Ở GIỮA ---\nrectangle \&quot;Ticket Vendor Machine (TVM) System\&quot; as tvm {\n    package \&quot;1. Core Ticketing\&quot; {\n        usecase \&quot;Select Language\&quot; as UC_Lang\n        usecase \&quot;Start &amp; Select Destination\&quot; as UC_Dest\n        usecase \&quot;Calculate Fare\&quot; as UC_Fare\n        usecase \&quot;Print Ticket\&quot; as UC_Ticket\n    }\n\n    package \&quot;2. Payment Processing\&quot; {\n        usecase \&quot;Make Payment\&quot; as UC_Pay\n        usecase \&quot;Pay via Credit Card\&quot; as UC_PayCC\n        usecase \&quot;Pay via QR Code\&quot; as UC_PayQR\n        usecase \&quot;Validate Payment\&quot; as UC_Validate\n        usecase \&quot;Print Receipt\&quot; as UC_Receipt\n        usecase \&quot;Cancel Transaction\&quot; as UC_Cancel\n    }\n\n    package \&quot;3. System &amp; Maintenance\&quot; {\n        usecase \&quot;Handle Errors &amp; Refund\&quot; as UC_Error\n        usecase \&quot;Remote Monitoring\&quot; as UC_Monitor\n        usecase \&quot;Transaction Logging\&quot; as UC_Log\n    }\n}\n\n&#39; --- BẮT BUỘC EXTERNAL ACTORS BÊN PHẢI ---\nactor \&quot;Payment Gateway\\n(Visa, MoMo...)\&quot; as gateway &lt;&lt;External&gt;&gt;\nactor \&quot;Maintenance Staff\&quot; as staff\nactor \&quot;Central System\&quot; as cms &lt;&lt;External&gt;&gt;\n\n&#39; Ép các Actor bên phải nằm thẳng hàng dọc với nhau\ngateway -[hidden]d- staff\nstaff -[hidden]d- cms\n\n&#39; --- ĐIỀU HƯỚNG MŨI TÊN (TỪ TRÁI QUA) ---\npassenger ---&gt; UC_Lang\npassenger ---&gt; UC_Dest\npassenger ---&gt; UC_Pay\npassenger ---&gt; UC_Cancel\n\n&#39; --- SỬA LẠI CÁC LIÊN KẾT NỘI BỘ (Để hệ thống tự bo góc tự nhiên) ---\nUC_Dest ..&gt; UC_Fare : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n&#39; Đổi thành &lt;.. để PlantUML tự sắp xếp mà không bị gãy góc\nUC_Pay &lt;.. UC_PayCC : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\nUC_Pay &lt;.. UC_PayQR : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\nUC_Pay ..&gt; UC_Validate : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\nUC_Pay ..&gt; UC_Ticket : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt; (success)\n\nUC_Ticket &lt;.. UC_Receipt : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt; (for CC)\nUC_Cancel &lt;.. UC_Error : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt; (printer error)\n\n&#39; --- ĐIỀU HƯỚNG MŨI TÊN (SANG PHẢI) ---\nUC_Validate ---&gt; gateway\nUC_Error ---&gt; staff\nUC_Monitor ---&gt; staff\nUC_Monitor ---&gt; cms\nUC_Log ---&gt; cms\n\n@enduml&quot;,&quot;format&quot;:&quot;svg&quot;}" id="eaQGf-tPn1OLxV2jsEUR-1">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="2235.16" width="6450.38" x="-4590" y="-1120" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml\n!theme spacelab\nskinparam roundcorner 10\nskinparam maxmessagesize 100\nskinparam wrapWidth 150\n\n&#39; --- ĐỊNH NGHĨA SWIMLANES VÀ MÀU SẮC ---\n|#E8F5E9|Passenger|\n|#FAFAFA|TVM System|\n|#E3F2FD|Payment Gateway|\n\n|Passenger|\nstart\n:Press \&quot;Start\&quot; button;\n\n|TVM System|\n:Display Destinations\\n(Bus / MRT);\n\n|Passenger|\n:Select Destination;\n\n|TVM System|\n:Calculate Fare\\n(Zone-based);\n\n&#39; --- VÒNG LẶP THANH TOÁN ---\nrepeat :Display Fare &amp; Prompt Payment;\n\n    |Passenger|\n    if (Payment Method?) then (Credit Card)\n        :Insert Credit Card;\n        |TVM System|\n        :Read Card Data;\n    else (QR Code)\n        |TVM System|\n        :Generate Dynamic QR\\n(Valid 3 mins);\n        |Passenger|\n        :Scan QR Code;\n    endif\n\n    |TVM System|\n    :Send Transaction Request;\n\n    |Payment Gateway|\n    :Process &amp; Validate;\n\n|TVM System|\nbackward:Prompt Retry;\nnote right: Session auto-cancels if\\nretries exceed 3 (FR-08)\\nor 60s timeout (FR-11)\nrepeat while (Payment Approved?) is (No)\n-&gt;Yes;\n\n&#39; --- XỬ LÝ LỖI PHẦN CỨNG HOẶC IN VÉ ---\nif (Printer Status?) then (Error / Jammed)\n    :Display Error Message;\n    :Send Refund Request;\n    \n    |Payment Gateway|\n    :Process Full Refund;\n    \n    |TVM System|\n    :Alert Maintenance Staff;\n    :Log Error &amp; Go Offline;\n    stop\nelse (Ready)\n    |TVM System|\n    \n    &#39; Xử lý đa luồng (Concurrent tasks)\n    fork\n        :Print Paper Ticket;\n    fork again\n        if (Paid via Credit Card?) then (Yes)\n            :Print Receipt;\n        else (No)\n        endif\n    fork again\n        :Log Transaction\\n(Central System);\n    end fork\n    \n    :Return to Home Screen;\n    stop\nendif\n\n@enduml&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="eaQGf-tPn1OLxV2jsEUR-9">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="2249.82" width="2441.24" x="1890" y="-1139.82" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&quot;data&quot;:&quot;@startuml\n!theme united\n\n\nskinparam roundcorner 10\nskinparam maxmessagesize 100\n\nactor Passenger as user\nparticipant \&quot;UI_TouchScreen\&quot; as ui\nparticipant \&quot;TransactionController\&quot; as controller\nparticipant \&quot;FareCalculator\&quot; as fareCalc\ndatabase \&quot;LocalDB\&quot; as db\nparticipant \&quot;PaymentGateway\&quot; as gateway &lt;&lt;External&gt;&gt;\nparticipant \&quot;HardwareManager\\n(Printer/CardReader)\&quot; as hw\n\nuser -&gt; ui : 1. Press \&quot;Start\&quot;\nactivate ui\nui -&gt; controller : 2. initSession()\nactivate controller\ncontroller -&gt; db : 3. fetchDestinations()\nactivate db\ndb --&gt; controller : list of destinations\ndeactivate db\ncontroller --&gt; ui : displayDestinations()\nui --&gt; user : Show Map &amp; Destinations\n\nuser -&gt; ui : 4. Select Destination\nui -&gt; controller : setDestination(destID)\ncontroller -&gt; fareCalc : 5. calculateFare(origin, destID)\nactivate fareCalc\nfareCalc --&gt; controller : fareAmount\ndeactivate fareCalc\ncontroller --&gt; ui : showFareAndPaymentMethods()\n\nuser -&gt; ui : 6. Select Payment (e.g., Credit Card)\nui -&gt; controller : initPayment(method)\n\nalt Credit Card Payment\n    controller -&gt; hw : activateCardReader()\n    activate hw\n    user -&gt; hw : Insert Card\n    hw -&gt; controller : cardData\n    deactivate hw\nelse QR Code Payment\n    controller -&gt; controller : generateDynamicQR()\n    controller --&gt; ui : displayQR()\n    user -&gt; ui : Scan QR with App\nend\n\ncontroller -&gt; gateway : 7. processPayment(amount, token)\nactivate gateway\ngateway --&gt; controller : paymentSuccess(transactionID)\ndeactivate gateway\n\ncontroller -&gt; hw : 8. printTicket(ticketDetails)\nactivate hw\nhw --&gt; controller : printStatus(success)\ndeactivate hw\n\ncontroller -&gt; db : 9. logTransaction(transactionID, status)\ncontroller --&gt; ui : displayThankYou()\nui --&gt; user : Dispense Ticket\ndeactivate controller\ndeactivate ui\n\n@enduml&quot;,&quot;format&quot;:&quot;svg&quot;}" id="eaQGf-tPn1OLxV2jsEUR-10">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="2194.63" width="1949.11" x="6820.89" y="-1160" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml\n!theme materia\nskinparam roundcorner 10\n\n[*] --&gt; Idle_State\n\nstate Idle_State {\n  Idle_State : Display Welcome Screen\n  Idle_State : Wait for User Input\n}\n\nstate Destination_Selection {\n  Destination_Selection : Display Bus/MRT map\n  Destination_Selection : Wait for choice\n}\n\nstate Fare_Calculation {\n  Fare_Calculation : Lookup zone pricing\n  Fare_Calculation : Display total amount\n}\n\nstate Payment_Processing {\n  Payment_Processing : Wait for Card/QR scan\n  Payment_Processing : Communicate with Gateway\n}\n\nstate Ticket_Dispensing {\n  Ticket_Dispensing : Print Paper Ticket\n  Ticket_Dispensing : Print Receipt (if CC)\n}\n\nstate Out_Of_Service {\n  Out_Of_Service : Display \&quot;Maintenance Required\&quot;\n  Out_Of_Service : Suspend operations\n}\n\nIdle_State --&gt; Destination_Selection : Press \&quot;Start\&quot;\nDestination_Selection --&gt; Fare_Calculation : Destination Selected\nFare_Calculation --&gt; Payment_Processing : Confirm Payment Method\n\nPayment_Processing --&gt; Ticket_Dispensing : Payment Approved\nPayment_Processing --&gt; Payment_Processing : Payment Failed [Retry &lt; 3]\nPayment_Processing --&gt; Idle_State : Payment Failed [Retry = 3]\n\nTicket_Dispensing --&gt; Idle_State : Ticket Printed Successfully\n\n&#39; Global Error and Timeout Transitions\nDestination_Selection --&gt; Idle_State : Timeout 60s\nFare_Calculation --&gt; Idle_State : Timeout 60s / Cancel\nPayment_Processing --&gt; Idle_State : Timeout 60s / Cancel\n\nIdle_State --&gt; Out_Of_Service : Hardware Fault Detected (e.g., Paper Jam)\nTicket_Dispensing --&gt; Out_Of_Service : Printer Error [Triggers Refund]\nOut_Of_Service --&gt; Idle_State : Staff Resolves Issue\n\n@enduml&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="eaQGf-tPn1OLxV2jsEUR-11">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="2231.06" width="2464.94" x="4380" y="-1139.82" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml\n!theme spacelab\nskinparam roundcorner 10\nskinparam classAttributeIconSize 0\nskinparam nodesep 50\nskinparam ranksep 50\n\nclass TVM {\n  - machineID: String\n  - locationData: String\n  - paperLevel: int\n  - currentStatus: MachineStatus\n  + startSession(): Session\n  + reportStatusToCentral(): void\n  + triggerMaintenanceAlert(): void\n}\n\nclass Session {\n  - sessionID: String\n  - startTime: DateTime\n  - isComplete: boolean\n  + selectDestination(dest: Destination): void\n  + cancelSession(): void\n  + checkTimeout(): boolean\n}\n\nclass Destination {\n  - destID: String\n  - name: String\n  - transportType: String\n  - zone: int\n  + getRouteInfo(): String\n}\n\nclass FareCalculator {\n  - baseFare: double\n  - zoneMultiplier: double\n  + calculateTotal(origin: String, dest: Destination): double\n}\n\nabstract class Payment {\n  - paymentID: String\n  - amount: double\n  - timestamp: DateTime\n  - status: PaymentStatus\n  + processTransaction(): boolean\n  + issueRefund(): boolean\n}\n\nclass CreditCardPayment {\n  - cardToken: String\n  - cardType: String\n  + readCardData(): void\n}\n\nclass QRCodePayment {\n  - qrCodeString: String\n  - walletProvider: String\n  - expiryTime: DateTime\n  + generateQR(): void\n  + verifyScan(): boolean\n}\n\nclass Ticket {\n  - ticketID: String\n  - origin: String\n  - destName: String\n  - validUntil: DateTime\n  - barcodeData: String\n  + generateBarcode(): void\n  + print(): boolean\n}\n\nclass Receipt {\n  - receiptID: String\n  - transactionRef: String\n  - maskedCardNum: String\n  + print(): boolean\n}\n\n&#39; Relationships\nTVM \&quot;1\&quot; *-- \&quot;0..*\&quot; Session : manages\nSession \&quot;1\&quot; --&gt; \&quot;1\&quot; Destination : targets\nSession \&quot;1\&quot; --&gt; \&quot;1\&quot; FareCalculator : uses\nSession \&quot;1\&quot; *-- \&quot;1\&quot; Payment : processes\nSession \&quot;1\&quot; *-- \&quot;1\&quot; Ticket : generates\nPayment &lt;|-- CreditCardPayment\nPayment &lt;|-- QRCodePayment\nCreditCardPayment \&quot;1\&quot; ..&gt; \&quot;0..1\&quot; Receipt : generates\n\n@enduml&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="eaQGf-tPn1OLxV2jsEUR-12">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="2280" width="1967.65" x="8770" y="-1160" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
